## Summary

‚úÖ **Fixed header colors** - Stress/Burnout 2/3 now shows RED (not orange)
‚úÖ **Consistent warning** - Any stress (1/3, 2/3, 3/3) = RED color
‚úÖ **Clear visual** - Only 0/3 (no stress) = GREEN, everything else = RED
‚úÖ **Simple logic** - Removed intermediate orange color for stress parameters
‚úÖ **Both components** - Background color AND text color both RED for Medium/High

**PDF reports now clearly show RED for any stress level (2/3 and 3/3)!** üéØ
